{"tid":25512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩夫婦為錢嘈交 妻燒炭變燒屋","createTime":"2016-12-06T07:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T08:19:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"566aceda69daa138acf870e21ab4ff55ace18f69","tid":25512,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161206/19856876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161206%2F19856876&d=DHJINZCkzmJxfC0bBCNoCnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a5c9a265\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161206%2F19856876&h=50aeddbb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161206/19856876</a><br />\n<br />\n兩夫婦為錢嘈交<br />\n妻燒炭變燒屋<br />\n<br />\n12,137<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】天水圍天瑞邨一對夫婦，前晚因金錢問題爭執，丈夫偕女兒離家到樓下暫避冷靜，至凌晨抬頭發現單位窗戶冒煙起火，趕回家揭發妻子在房間內燒炭自殺，火舌燃著雜物引起火警，兩夫婦俱吸入濃煙不適送院，燒炭變燒屋毀家園。<br />\n<br />\n女事主姓吳（44歲），與姓盧（45歲）丈夫及22歲女兒，同住天瑞邨瑞滿樓一單位。據悉，吳婦有情緒病，前晚10時，吳婦與丈夫因金錢問題爭執，情緒激動，盧為了息事寧人，偕女兒離家落街暫避，讓妻子冷靜一下。<br />\n<br />\n至昨凌晨零時許，盧抬頭乍見自己單位的窗戶冒出濃煙，冷氣機起火，立即趕回寓所了解，發現妻子在房間內燒炭自殺，燃燒了旁邊的雜物，引起火警，鄰居亦見單位冒出濃煙，紛紛報警求助。消防員到場開喉撲救，約26分鐘將火救熄，其間疏散約150名居民往樓下。火警中吳婦與丈夫俱吸入濃煙不適，送院後吳婦情況穩定。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n必勝客速遞員炒車亡<br />\n下一則<br />\n街頭遇襲被打爆頭　血人衝入7仔求救"},{"pid":"873debecd52af37ea4f93dc5d2f2d47cf0761313","tid":25512,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20161206/org/1480965035_c271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20161206%2Forg%2F1480965035_c271.jpg&h=39aedc6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"197d68520a24f3e53c6633217fa8d6737167036e","tid":25512,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"又燒屋自剎"},{"pid":"d96e7c52db5fe81252722e45efdbaa1abe22e990","tid":25512,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:06:03.000Z","msg":"又係天水圍"},{"pid":"8064b684c2f4ce57a02aee66726812f395eef25f","tid":25512,"uid":54654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"笨撚柒，我想說聲恭喜呀"},{"pid":"2e265414ec899705365a8b0f13c04d7ba6ef3fa9","tid":25512,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"樓上那戶真係多得佢唔少"},{"pid":"8bf07115facc95994673c5491e39f3eea561fa79","tid":25512,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:24:35.000Z","msg":"有冇 22歲女兒 圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdae3ba4cb6b8049b8b9879e43f2dd0657b5e598","tid":25512,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:28:08.000Z","msg":"想換屋都唔洗燒屋喎。"},{"pid":"eba3520c020cfd213b30666aa835eec61279e6e7","tid":25512,"uid":14738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:23:33.000Z","msg":"又要為錢嘈多次交"},{"pid":"6c6e652c5526246b123d7f7929975106f5013891","tid":25512,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:05:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e080e08a8ef83893dbdcd0256711c02d13bd8623","tid":25512,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"又係天水圍"},{"pid":"931d2757b36a34b9bf9ab64c4edaafd12c0a35ad","tid":25512,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上那戶真係多得佢唔少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下個月就過年，樓上好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}